00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:17,400
Special Report:
Tachibana Hideo

178
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:17,400
Meiwa Ichi 
High School's
 Second-Year
 Clean-Up Hitter

179
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:17,400
In his first-at bat, a homerun to
the middle of the left-field stands.
A hero makes a flashy debut at 
the Koushien.

180
00:12:15,180 --> 00:12:16,270
Hmm.

181
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:19,910
Hmm.

182
00:12:22,740 --> 00:12:24,330
Hide-chan is amazing.

183
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:30,000
This is nothing, given his talent.

184
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:33,600
If you feel frustrated, you should make your way into the newspaper, too.

185
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,700
I'm in it already.

186
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:35,600
Huh ?

187
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:43,550
Where ?

188
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,000
"Friend A" ?

189
00:12:49,650 --> 00:12:53,590
"He had always been on a different level than us."

190
00:12:53,590 --> 00:12:56,150
"For us, the Koushien is
 a dream within a dream."

191
00:12:56,150 --> 00:13:00,900
"But for Tachibana, it's just the 
first step in his baseball career."

192
00:13:00,900 --> 00:13:04,700
"I'm proud of the fact that I was once Tachibana's teammate."

193
00:13:05,300 --> 00:13:06,990
Who said anything like this ?!

194
00:13:11,250 --> 00:13:12,150
Hello.

195
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,000
Hello.

196
00:13:13,900 --> 00:13:16,010
Is this the home of "Friend A" ?

197
00:13:16,010 --> 00:13:16,990
Hey...!

198
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:26,000
Koushien

199
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:26,000
Stadium

200
00:13:21,230 --> 00:13:23,920
Hiro, the Koushien is amazing.

201
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:25,450
Huh ?

202
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:31,000
Because it's amazing, way too amazing, you have to see it with your own eyes.

203
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:33,630
What are you talking about ?

204
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:37,480
Work hard, and come here this summer.

205
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:43,270
This summer, come 
to the Koushien, Hiro.

206
00:13:44,090 --> 00:13:45,350
Yeah.

207
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:48,840
Well, the second-round game is starting.

208
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:03,850
Hit it, hit it, Tachibana !

209
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:07,500
Hit it, hit it, Tachibana !

210
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:10,940
Hit it, hit it, Tachibana !

211
00:14:11,370 --> 00:14:14,510
Hit it, hit it, Tachibana !

212
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:18,100
Hit it, hit it, Tachibana !

213
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:21,800
Hit it, hit it, Tachibana !

214
00:14:33,490 --> 00:14:36,030
You looked at the fastball up and in.

215
00:14:36,700 --> 00:14:41,470
In the batter's box is Tachibana Hideo, 
the slugger from powerhouse Meiwa Ichi.

216
00:14:41,470 --> 00:14:44,650
Now, on the mound is 
Senkawa's ace pitcher, Kunimi.

217
00:14:44,650 --> 00:14:46,350
What will he throw next ?

218
00:14:47,620 --> 00:14:49,120
Am I in the way ?

219
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:52,000
You were imagining yourself at the Koushien, right ?

220
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:56,760
You're early. Practice
 doesn't start until afternoon.

221
00:14:56,760 --> 00:15:00,710
As I was watching TV at home, I couldn't sit still.

222
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:01,700
You, too ?

223
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:02,220
I guess.

224
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,650


225
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:06,940
What is it ?

226
00:15:07,310 --> 00:15:09,800
No, nothing, really.

227
00:15:11,850 --> 00:15:13,100
You're weird.

228
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:14,620
Hey, Hiro !

229
00:15:14,970 --> 00:15:17,220
Hey !

230
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:22,650
We, the Senkawa Baseball Club, have great team chemistry.

231
00:15:24,550 --> 00:15:25,860
Hey, thanks for the wait !

232
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:30,200
Genius Kine Ryutarou has arrived !

233
00:15:30,900 --> 00:15:32,350
No one was waiting for you.

234
00:15:32,830 --> 00:15:33,550


235
00:15:33,550 --> 00:15:37,830
Kunimi, let's all go 
together, to the Koushien.

236
00:15:37,830 --> 00:15:40,330
Yeah, including you.

237
00:15:43,710 --> 00:15:46,100
Well, let's do some work !

238
00:15:46,550 --> 00:15:47,330
I...

239
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:51,880
...hate high school baseball.

240
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,290
Principal...

241
00:15:53,290 --> 00:15:55,540
I can't focus on my work.

242
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:57,550
I see.

243
00:15:58,890 --> 00:16:02,000
In summer, it'll
 probably get even worse.

244
00:16:02,660 --> 00:16:05,700
I can totally guarantee that.

245
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:15,400
Homerun !

246
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,700
Right at the back screen...

247
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:20,400
...a three-run homer to even up the score, coming back from a hopeless situation.

248
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,700
Listen to the crowd cheering.

249
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:24,300
With their back against the 
wall in the bottom of the ninth...

250
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:30,650
...Tachibana's homerun sends this game into the third extra inning game of this tournament.

251
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:26,040
It's hot.

252
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:28,050
My chest feels hot.

253
00:16:28,050 --> 00:16:30,650
The passionate feelings turn into cheers...

254
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:33,090
...and it becomes a big swell 
that envelopes the Koushien.

255
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:37,190
The voices, the commotion...

256
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,980
It's amazing.
It really is amazing, Hiro.

257
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,000
The Koushien unites everyone.

258
00:17:01,150 --> 00:17:02,000
Come.

259
00:17:02,830 --> 00:17:04,670
Come here, Hiro.

260
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:14,800
Kunimi.

261
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:17,730
It must be hard on him now.

